# Source-level overrides.
#
# We use 3.0 (quilt) because the changelog declares a Debian revision
# (1.0.0-1, latest entry). Native format would forbid the revision and
# dpkg-source -b would refuse the build. Quilt is the standard
# Debian/Astra source format and supports the upstream + Debian-revision
# split cleanly.
# lintian normally does not warn when format is explicit, so this file
# is intentionally a placeholder - re-evaluate after a real `lintian`
# run on Ubuntu 22.04 / Astra SE and remove it if it never fires.
